<span foreground='$BMAGENTA' >    TODO Weekdays </span> 
<span foreground='$RED' >    -=-=-=-=-=-=-</span> 
<span foreground='$BLUE'>1. </span>The Shellcoder's <span foreground='$FG'></span>
<span foreground='$BLUE'>2. </span>The Hack Art     <span foreground='$FG'></span>
<span foreground='$BLUE'>3. </span>Comp Netw        <span foreground='$FG'></span>
<span foreground='$BLUE'>4. </span>Javascript       <span foreground='$FG'></span>
<span foreground='$BLUE'>5. </span>Openssl          <span foreground='$FG'></span>
<span foreground='$BLUE'>6. </span>*NIX Stuff       <span foreground='$FG'></span>
<span foreground='$BLUE'>7. </span>Metasploitable   <span foreground='$FG'></span>
<span foreground='$BLUE'>8. </span>Master C         <span foreground='$FG'></span>
</span>
"
